text: == Events == * Change of emperor of the Ottoman Empire from Osman I (1299-1326) to Orhan I (1326-1359) * Aradia de Toscano, is initiated into a Dianic cult of Italian Witchcraft (Stregheria), and discovers through a vision that she is the human incarnation of the goddess Aradia. Known as La Bella Pelegrina amongst the outlaws near Lake Nemi, she becomes the leader of a religious anarchist movement.
